## Terraform

# Ignore Terraform working directories
**/.terraform/*

# Ignore lock file since this is a sample repo.
.terraform.lock.hcl

# Ignore override files
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# Ignore crash logs generated by Terraform in case of an error
crash.log

# Ignore variable definition files, often containing sensitive information (credentials, etc.) but allow terraform.sample.tfvars
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
!terraform.sample.tfvars

# Ignore Terraform plan output files
*.tfplan

# Ignore local configuration for Terraform CLI
.terraformrc
.terraform.d/

# Ignore backup files created by Terraform when modifying state
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.backup
